==================
Pomodoro-Indicator
==================

Pomodoro-Indicator an indicator to work with the Pomodoro Technique

For more information, please visit our website:
http://www.atareao.es/apps/la-tecnica-pomodoro-en-ubuntu-con-pomodoro-indicator/
or
http://www.atareao.es

============
Requirements
============

Required dependencies:

    gir1.2-gtk-3.0,
    gir1.2-gdkpixbuf-2.0,
    gir1.2-gstreamer-1.0,
    gir1.2-gst-plugins-base-1.0,
    gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1,
    gir1.2-notify-0.7,
    python3,
    python3-gi,
    python3-dbus

========
Download
========

Download the code:

    $ git clone https://github.com/atareao/pomodoro-indicator.git

=======
Install
=======

    $ sudo add-apt-repository ppa:atareao/atareao
    $ sudo apt-get update
    $ sudo apt-get install pomodoro-indicator
